# screenshot-mcp rules for Windsurf

This is the screenshot-mcp project. Key facts:

- Entry point: `bin/screenshot-mcp.js` (CLI + MCP server)
- MCP server command: `node bin/screenshot-mcp.js serve`
- Platform logic: `src/screenshot.js` — Linux (X11/Wayland), macOS, Windows
- Tool installers: `src/install.js` — adds MCP config to AI tools

When editing screenshot backends, always try multiple tool binaries in order and
throw a clear error listing what to install if all fail. Never assume a specific
tool is present on the user's machine.
